profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.

profile:
Riverside Renos is a locally owned general contracting company serving the Greater Muskoka Area.  Our dedicated team is well versed in the lifestyle and the unique needs of the cottage community.  We offer a wide variety of services including the construction and installation of custom docks and decks, custom interiors, exterior additions and new construction. At Riverside Renos, you will work alongside our team who will help bring your vision to life, providing an upfront and detailed quote as well as an organized timeline for your project(s).  With a reputation that speaks for itself, our hardworking team is ready to fulfill your design dreams.     
                                                                                                                              
                  
Below are some of the services we offer:
          
• Custom Decks
• Custom Docks: Floating Systems, Pole Systems, Tower Dock Systems, Custom Aluminum Construction, etc.
• Custom Interiors: Basement, Kitchen, Bathroom, Flooring, etc.
• Exterior Additions
• New Construction

Looking for Recommended Handyman Services in the Simcoe Muskoka Region? Look No Further!
Not everyone has the expertise to tackle those tricky home renovations or overdue cottage repairs by themselves. With Agnew Contracting on board, completing that work in the shortest amount of time has never been simpler.

About Us
My name is Tyler, and I’m the owner-operator of Agnew Contracting, along with my wife, Janelle. In business since 2019, Agnew Contracting is all about making your home renovations easy and worry-free. I enjoy helping people improve the value, comfort, and appearance of their property. My company’s carpentry expertise and courteous handyman services have kept us busy over the years. Thankfully, we love what we do!

profile: Upper Lakes Property Management is a full-service maintenance provider for luxury cottages, homes, multi-unit commercial and residential properties in the Muskoka Lakes region and surrounding area. profile:
Welcome to SBC Construction Management. We will aim to take the stress out of building your project. If it is a long-distance relationship, where a daily or even weekly site visit isn’t always an option, or even local, our aim is to make your
building experience enjoyable. Along with our Design Team, we will coordinate with Interior Designers, Engineers, local Building Departments and the MNR and Forestry, and will organize your project professionally, from concept to completion.

Services:

Plan, Design, Construction Care

At SBC, and as the owner the of the company, I believe that part of your expectations, includes providing you with my personnel individual expertice in both construction management, design and more importantly my 35 plus years as a carpenter. It is because of my experience as a carpenter, that I am able to see all aspects of your project in fine detail. It is because of this experience, management of your project will be more effective without compromising the quality.

Yours truly and thank you,​​​​​

James C. Hildebrandt
